              <span id="reviewTextContainer469137127" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8642468333657911534">Ok, I was trying to judbe a book by its cover when I decided that I wanted to read this book. I mean, OMG this book&apos;s cover is gorgeous. The second thing that grabbed me were the comparisons to The Hunger Games.<br/><br/>I&apos;m one of the few people that haven&apos;t read that series, but I&apos;ve not heard much bad about it, so I figured I&apos;d give this book a go, and I&apos;m glad I did.<br/><br/>Very action packed and a quick read. Great YA for fantasy lovers or for someone looking for something different to read. I didn&apos;t find th</span>
  <span id="freeText8642468333657911534" style="display:none">Ok, I was trying to judbe a book by its cover when I decided that I wanted to read this book. I mean, OMG this book's cover is gorgeous. The second thing that grabbed me were the comparisons to The Hunger Games.<br /><br />I'm one of the few people that haven't read that series, but I've not heard much bad about it, so I figured I'd give this book a go, and I'm glad I did.<br /><br />Very action packed and a quick read. Great YA for fantasy lovers or for someone looking for something different to read. I didn't find the comparisons to The Hunger Games to be accurate from what I've heard of the other series, but the story was definitely engaging and the ending left me eagerly wanting the next book.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8642468333657911534" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
