<span id="freeTextContainer2521680550581016035">This book ROCKED, Seriously!! It is so full of action &amp; adventure that I literally could not put the book down! The plot was so engaging and unique! The characters were so well written that you can not help but root for them! There are some really interesting creatures as well! I highly recommend this book to young and old alike..you will not be disappointed! It is one of my favorite YA books! I am eagerly awaiting book 2!! </span>

